The methods of this embodiment can be practiced using compounds having the general structure (III). Preferred methods employ compounds that have been empirically determined to exhibit at least 10-fold selective inhibition of PI3Kδ relative to other PI3K isoforms. For example, the methods can be practiced using the following compounds:


